title: Call of Duty 4 Sounds
description:
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------

All content (excluding the .caf files) has been found on http://www.acegames.us/forum/free-sms-ringtones/35205-call-duty-4-sounds.html.


The .caf files are from http://modmyi.com/forums/ringtone-alert-sounds/376231-call-duty-4-sounds-sliders-works-winterboard.html

---------------------------------------------------------------------------

The collection consists of 314 quotes and popular sayings, most to be found on the online multiplayer, but there are some from the offline singleplayer aswell.
There are one or two songs(winning themes) and VERY few explosions or gun effects (only AK47 and claymore, I think).

The quality may not be the outmost best, but it satisfies my standards. Especially if you have planned to use it on your mobile phone as intended.

Examples:
"Our UAV is online!",
"GRANATA!", 
"Cover me, I am reloading!", 
"Poppin' smoke!", 
"50,000 people used to live here..." 



this is my first torrent ever, feel free to comment or warn me if something is wrong.

thanks
